headline: Zimmer Biomet Launches You'll Be Back Campaign with Chief Movement Officer Arnold Schwarzenegger
summary: Zimmer Biomet Holdings, Inc. (NYSE and SIX: ZBH), a global medical technology leader, today announced the launch of the You'll Be Back campaign with the Company's Chief Movement Officer, Arnold Schwarzenegger. The goal of the You'll Be Back campaign is to provide the millions of people living with joint pain an online community that empowers them with resources to make informed choices about their mobility. headline: Zimmer Biomet Announces Quarterly Dividend for First Quarter of 2025
summary: Zimmer Biomet Holdings, Inc. (NYSE and SIX: ZBH), a global medical technology leader, today announced that its Board of Directors has approved the payment of a quarterly cash dividend to stockholders for the first quarter of 2025. The cash dividend of $0.24 per share is payable on or about April 30, 2025 to stockholders of record as of the close of business on March 31, 2025.
